Great British Menu - Series 10, Episodes 26 to 30




North West

Representing the north west of England are Eve Townson, Matt Worswick and returning contender Mark Ellis. And after failing to cook for the judges in 2014, Mark's out to redeem himself. But he faces stiff competition in executive chef Eve and young gun Matt.




Original Air Dates: 14-Sep-2015 to 18-Sep-2015
